data.name: labelRelativeStatValuesWarning.Text
data.value: WARNING: Relative Stat Values (also known as EP values) are *not* an accurate way to compare gear / gems / enchants / buffs / etc. They are especially inaccurate regarding any stat with caps (such as hit rating). They are provided here for convenience, but please remember that comparing in Rawr will always be more accurate. If you do choose to use these, please be sure to update them every time any of your stats change, in order to maintain any semblance of accuracy.
